Description: Index of fishing effort (instantaneous per season)
Fishing mortality by time, age, fleet, region, stock
Seasonal abundance without incoming recruitment (after survival and movement)
Seasonal abundance (incoming recruitment and advancing age class when $m = m_{\textrm{rec}}$)
Equation: $N_{y,m,a,r',s} = \begin{cases} R_{y,s} \textrm{mov}_{y,m,1,r,r',s} & a = 1\\ \sum_r N_{y,m-1,a-1,r,s}\exp(-Z_{y,m-1,a-1,r,s}) \textrm{mov}_{y,m,a,r,r',s} & a = 2, \ldots, A-1\\ \sum_{a'=A-1}^A\sum_r N_{y,m-1,a',r,s}\exp(-Z_{y,m-1,a',r,s})\textrm{mov}_{y,m,a,r,r',s} & a = A\end{cases}$
